title: Two master bedrooms with walk in closets and bath + guest powder room
posting_body: ['%&$Experience Exclusive Island in Brickell at prestigious Tequesta II Building.', 'Enjoy Spectacular Bay, Ocean and City views from large balcony and all rooms.', 'Brickell Key has restaurants, market and hotel.', 'Building has 24 hours security/concierge and valet service.', 'Beautiful 2/2.5 apartment.', 'Spacious Apt has Foyer entrance, formal dining, living room, eat-in kitchen with updated SS appliances, Split floor plan.', 'Two master bedrooms with walk in closets and bath + guest powder room.', '2 Parking spaces.', 'Gated island and building with state of the art waterfront two story gym, large pool, sauna, massage room, indoor racketball, tennis and Bball courts, BBQ area, party room, conference room,%$&', '#$%If you have been denied an application for lease in the past due to bad credit or your background, please call me or text me', 'show contact info', ', I will get you approved!!', 'Self-employed, bad credit, no problem.', 'Text me, I respond immediately and have tons of inventory!', 'WE ARE ESSENTIAL BUSINESS FOR COVI19, WE ARE ALWAYS OPEN', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'Andy Zamudio', 'show contact info', 'We accept deposits with credit card if you are short of cash we help with that, we are the only company that accepts credit cards for deposits , zelle, cash app, paypal venmo payments accepted!!!', 'Aceptamos los depositos con tarjeta de credito sinud esta corto de cash, somos la unica compañia que lo acepta en Florida, zelle, cash app, paypal ,venmo.']
